#### Q61. What will this code log to the console?

```
// File: person.js
exports.name = "Jane";

// File: index.js
const person = require('./person.js');
console.log(person);
```

- %OPTION% `{'Jane'}`
- %OPTION% `{ name: 'Jane' }`
- %OPTION% `{}`
- %OPTION% `Jane`

